c moments (AMM) of the\nnucleons, and compared to the results when the AMMs of nucleons are not taken\ninto account. The effects of magnetic field as well as isospin asymmetry on the\nupsilon masses are obserevd to be large at high densities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Jul 2018 16:19:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-25"}
