 over different wall-parallel wavenumber pairs. Our approach does\nnot rely on costly stochastic simulations and it provides insight into\nmechanisms for perturbation growth including the interaction of the slowly\nvarying base flow with streaks and Tollmien-Schlichting waves.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 20 Jul 2018 09:44:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Jun 2019 23:45:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-09"}
