s and Huber's scatter matrix $M$-estimators with respect to the CSCRB.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 20 Jul 2018 12:35:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Oct 2018 09:57:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-26"}
